{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pytorch/pytorch/issues/comments/326025590", "html_url": "https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/2573#issuecomment-326025590", "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pytorch/pytorch/issues/2573", "id": 326025590, "node_id": "MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDMyNjAyNTU5MA==", "user": {"login": "apaszke", "id": 4583066, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ1ODMwNjY=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/4583066?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke", "html_url": "https://github.com/apaszke", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/apaszke/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "created_at": "2017-08-30T15:23:16Z", "updated_at": "2017-08-30T15:23:16Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "body_html": "<p>It's because <code>a</code> is no longer a leaf Variable after calling <code>.cuda()</code> on it (its value is a result of a CPU -&gt; GPU transfer). Change</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-python\"><pre>a <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> Variable(torch.rand(<span class=\"pl-c1\">5</span>,<span class=\"pl-c1\">5</span>), <span class=\"pl-v\">requires_grad</span><span class=\"pl-k\">=</span><span class=\"pl-c1\">True</span>).cuda()</pre></div>\n<p>to</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-python\"><pre>a <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> Variable(torch.rand(<span class=\"pl-c1\">5</span>,<span class=\"pl-c1\">5</span>).cuda(), <span class=\"pl-v\">requires_grad</span><span class=\"pl-k\">=</span><span class=\"pl-c1\">True</span>)</pre></div>", "body_text": "It's because a is no longer a leaf Variable after calling .cuda() on it (its value is a result of a CPU -> GPU transfer). Change\na = Variable(torch.rand(5,5), requires_grad=True).cuda()\nto\na = Variable(torch.rand(5,5).cuda(), requires_grad=True)", "body": "It's because `a` is no longer a leaf Variable after calling `.cuda()` on it (its value is a result of a CPU -> GPU transfer). Change \r\n```python\r\na = Variable(torch.rand(5,5), requires_grad=True).cuda()\r\n```\r\nto\r\n```python\r\na = Variable(torch.rand(5,5).cuda(), requires_grad=True)\r\n```"}